condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1.2.3(b) | Description :The Borrower shall undertake semi-annual internal audits for DPWH'soperations and Project accounts. | Frequency :SemiAnnual
Finance Agreement :Section 1. 11 | Description :The Borrower shall submit a progress report on implementing the IntegrityStrengthening Action Plan. | Due Date :31-Oct-2011

Finance Agreement :Section 1.10 | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that amendments updating the operations andresponsibilities of the Road Board will be approved by DPWH and the Department of Transport and Communications. | Due Date:31-Mar-2011
Finance Agreement :Section 1.12 | Description :The Borrower shall complete the implementation of recommendations arising from its2006 external audit report. | Due Date :30-Jun-2011

Finance Agreement :Section 1.5 | Description :The Borrower shall implement its Rationalization Plan after approval by DBM in theevent that the Rationalization Plan is not put in to effect, develop a plan. | Due Date :31-Oct-2011

Finance Agreement :Section 1.6 | Description :The Borrower through DPWH shall post the Road Watch report cards on its website byNovember 30, 2009, and biannually on November 30 thereafter. | Due Date :30-Nov-2011

Finance Agreement :Section 1.7 | Description :Within one month, the Borrower shall publish a business plan comprising of itsproposed annual program for next year and the expenditure incurred and outputs delivered in the previous year. | Due Date:31-Dec-2009
Finance Agreement :Section 1.8 | Description :The Borrower through DPWH shall furnish to the Road Partners a road assetspreservation plan for the national road networks. | Due Date :31-Mar-2012

Finance Agreement :Section II. B.1 | Description :Maintain a financial management system and prepare financial statements inaccordance with consistently applied accounting standards | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Section II. B.2 | Description :Furnish quarterly interim unaudited financial report to the Bank, not later thanone month after each calendar quarter | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Section II. B.3 | Description :Financial statements to be audited by independent auditors acceptable to the Bankand audit report submitted to the Bank not later than six month after the end of each fiscal year. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement: Section 1.4. The Borrower shall undertake technical audits on Project expenditures and implementation of Projectactivities. | Frequency: Semi-Annual
